data.description: The DJ Khaled x Air Jordan 5 Retro ‘Crimson Bliss’ sees a classic silhouette through a new lens, in his ‘We the Best’ collection. The upper in a vibrant coral leather is contrasted with a silky quilted lining in Leche Blue, with the heel overlays adorned with a blue embroidered Nike Air logo on the right and 'We the Best' on the left. The silver reflective tongue features the classic Jumpman branding, and the translucent rubber outsoles complete the playful logo treatment with additional Jumpman and ‘We the Best’ branding. Underfoot, an off-white polyurethane midsole with blue speckled shark-tooth detailing is complemented by a visible Air-sole unit in the heel.

data.shoeName: Jordan 5 Retro DJ Khaled We The Best Sail
data.description: The DJ Khaled x Air Jordan 5 Retro ‘Sail' uses pastel hues and subtle logo highlights for its part in the ‘We the Best’ capsule collection. An off-white leather upper is highlighted by pastel embellishments and a powder-blue quilted lining, contrasting with the Air-assisted polyurethane midsole in Violet Star. The tongue features the classic Jumpman logo against a reflective silver finish, with 'Keep Going' hidden on its interior side. The two heel overlays contrast, with one adorned by the Nike Air log while the other proclaiming 'We the Best,' which also decorates the right shoe's translucent rubber outsole.

The black upper in nubuck features a metallic silver Swoosh accented by piping in royal blue; additional Swooshes embellish the toe box and tongue. The heel is adorned with a stitched 1Cent logo. data.description: Honoring the origins of Zoom Air techology is the Nike Air Zoom Flight 95 ‘Black Valerian Blue.’ In this pair, a Zoom Air unit appears on the forefoot with an Air-sole unit in the heel within a chunky Phylon midsole. data.shoeName: adidas Forum Buckle Low Bad Bunny Last Forum
data.description: Bad Bunny and adidas join up again to reinvent an iconic basketball silhouette. Two sets of overlapping tongues feature Bad Bunny ‘third eye’ branding. The sneaker rides on a traditional rubber cupsole with clear rubber sidewalls.

data.shoeName: Jordan 11 Retro Cherry (2022) (TD)

data.shoeName: Jordan 11 Retro Cherry (2022) (PS)

data.shoeName: UGG Classic Ultra Mini Chestnut (W)
